(Corrects name of company in first paragraph.)  New Hampshire Insurance Co. may
probe whether a “rogue trader” was an employee of MF Global
Holdings Ltd. as part of a lawsuit over liabilities for losses
tied to the company’s collapse, a  New York  state appeals court
ruled today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
